- Meteorologists are experts in the field of weather forecasting and are likely to make more accurate observations than non-experts.

sql:
SELECT name
FROM cyclones
ORDER BY name ASC;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT cyclone_id) AS hurricane_cyclone_count
FROM cyclone_status_changes
WHERE new_status = 'HURRICANE';

